1. Audience mismatch - wrong seniority/industry targeting
2. Ad-to-LP messaging disconnect - promise vs form mismatch
3. Wrong LP routing - sending to non-relevant landing page
4. LinkedIn: confirm utm_audience maps to Ad Set level (NOT Campaign Group level)
   ? seniority/company-size filters are at Ad Set (utm_audience), confirm UTM passthrough in HubSpot

